  "title": "Senior Graphic Designer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Work closely with project team and print production teams to ensure designs are optimized for efficient and high-quality printing.    </li>\n  <li>Understand different printing methods, material types, finishes, and techniques to create designs suitable for each project.  </li>\n  <li>Provide creative direction and leadership to the design team, guiding designers and ensuring high-quality design output.   </li>\n  <li>Manage and coordinate multiple design projects simultaneously, ensuring deadlines and quality standards are met.   </li>\n  <li>Approach design challenges with creativity, innovation, and the ability to propose alternative solutions.   </li>\n  <li>Fluency in current graphic design practices; such as Adobe Photoshop; Adobe Illustrator and Adobe InDesign.</li>\n</ul>",
